subtitleNullable: A dataset containing manually selected images of some One Piece characters.
descriptionNullable:
## Goal 

After designing an image classification model, the next step is to create a One Piece character detector to which this classifier will be applied.

## Data collection 
- Sources : Google search, Bing search 

## Contents info

- Contains some transformed images, using various techniques 
- Some images have been manually cropped to remove unnecessary noise

The folders contain approximately 650 images of : Luffy, Zoro, Sanji, Nami, Franky, Brook, Chopper, Usopp, Jinbei, Robin, Ace, Law, Shanks, Kurohige, Mihawk, Rayleigh. 

**I do not own these images.**

## Acknowledgements 
- ImageMagick tool :  which helped me correct some png profiles 
- EdiKer : which helped me augment a part of the data
